This is the new isotope site rails 3 project.

To get started:

	Create a gemset  "rvm gemset create isotope-rails3"
	Use the gemset   "rvm use 1.9.2@isotope-rails3"
	Install bundler  "gem install bundler"
	Run the bundle   "bundle install"
	Create the database "rake db:create"
	Run database migrations "rake db:migrate"
